Ar isslmad Lislam is rbbi iga yan d ur illi kra n rbbi bla [[Allah]] (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] : الله), d is iga [[Muḥmmad]] {{saw}} arqqas nns iggz fllas [[Lquran]] s tɣarast n unglus [[Jibril]] [[Afaylu:La_bracket.png|link=|20x20px]][[Afaylu:عليه_السلام.png|link=|20x20px|عليه السلام]][[Afaylu:Ra_bracket.png|link=|20x20px]]. tga tugtt n [[Imaziɣen|imaziɣn]] imuslmn.

